## mifu & metaphilosophy

# the ingredients[^1]

- tofoo naked tofu, x1 280g pack
- spring greens, 250g
- beansprouts, 200g
- edamame beans, 100g 
- schwartz thai seven spice, to taste
- chopped ginger, two thumbs
- chopped garlic, four cloves
- light soy sauce, to taste
- yutaka white miso paste, 50g
- rice vinegar, 4tbsp
- sesame seed oil, 4tbsp
- basmati rice, two portions




[^1]: i'm going to try & be as specific as possible with brands etc. because i know it's annoying not having enough detail sometimes!
